file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Test Query Parameters
  license:
    name: MIT
servers:
  - url: https://example.com
paths:
  /form/test-primitive:
    get:
      summary: Test passing primitive query parameters
      parameters:
        - name: id
          in: query
          description: Not required
          required: false
          schema:
            type: integer
        - name: id2
          in: query
          description: Required but nullable (nullable should be ignored)
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
            nullable: true
        - name: id3
          in: query
          description: Required and not nullable
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Empty response
    post:
      summary: Inlining simple queries
      parameters:
        - name: name
          in: query
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Empty response
    patch:
      summary: Inlining more complex queries (with an enum)
      parameters:
        - name: type
          in: query
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            enum:
              - cat
              - dog
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Empty response
  /form/test-array:
    get:
      summary: Form Array Explode True
      parameters:
        - name: type
          in: query
          required: true
          style: form
          explode: true
          schema:
            type: array
            items: 
              type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Empty response
    post:
      summary: Form Array Explode False
      parameters:
        - name: type
          in: query
          required: true
          style: form
          explode: false
          schema:
            type: array
            items: 
              type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Empty response
  /form/test-object:
    get:
      summary: Form Object Explode True
      parameters:
        - name: type
          in: query
          required: true
          style: form
          explode: true # default
          schema:
            type: object
            properties:
              id:
                type: string
              name:
                type: string
            required:
              - id
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Empty response
    post:
      summary: Form Object Explode False
      parameters:
        - name: type
          in: query
          required: true
          style: form
          explode: false
          schema:
            type: object
            properties:
              id:
                type: string
              name:
                type: string
            required:
              - id
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Empty response
  /delimeters/test-array:
    get:
      summary: Space Delimited Explode False
      parameters:
        - name: type
          in: query
          required: true
          style: spaceDelimited
          explode: false
          schema:
            type: array
            items: 
              type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Empty response
    post:
      summary: Pipe Delimited Explode False
      parameters:
        - name: type
          in: query
          required: false
          style: pipeDelimited
          explode: false
          schema:
            type: array
            items: 
              type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Empty response
    put:
      summary: Space Delimited Explode True
      parameters:
        - name: type
          in: query
          required: true
          style: spaceDelimited
          explode: true # default
          schema:
            type: array
            items: 
              type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Empty response
    patch:
      summary: Pipe Delimited Explode True
      parameters:
        - name: type
          in: query
          required: false
          style: pipeDelimited
          explode: true # default
          schema:
            type: array
            items: 
              type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Empty response
  /deep-object:
    get:
      summary: Form Object Explode False
      parameters:
        - name: type
          in: query
          required: true
          style: deepObject
          schema:
            type: object
            properties:
              id:
                type: string
              name:
                type: string
            required:
              - id
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Empty response
